 next few weeks you ll be able to spend more time building relationships with your teammates and supervisor we want you to feel confident and prepared for your new career at slac the following checklists will assist new employees new employees should review the new employee checklist administrative assistants should review the slac admin associate handbook managers who need to onboard new employees should review the onboarding checklist to assist you in giving your new employee a rewarding experience as s he is welcomed into the slac workforce links new employee action steps new employee orientation and training resources additional resources for new employees contact information for information about new employee orientation sessions or the onboarding process please contact maria mastrokyriakos your browser does not have the ability to display inline frames you can view the content of this frame at this page slac footer your browser does not have the ability to display inline frames you can view the content of this frame at this page slac global navigation header top last update
